    "attributes": {
        "action": "Include Polish as a language option in the national curriculum",
        "additional_details": "I would like for this to happen as there are a lot of Polish people in the country. Learning Polish could help greet and say simple sentences like \"I can't speak Polish but I'll find someone that can for you to help you\" with Polish people that don't know English. This would really help Polish people as not everyone has a translator with them.",
        "background": "I would like Polish to be added as a modern language option within the national curriculum as this is a language that is used a lot in the UK. Learning it, could help greet Polish people who can't speak English well.",
